{"tid":623370,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【歐聯】不屑紅軍踢法 費蘭甸奴：咪又係長傳急攻","createTime":"2018-04-10T02:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T10:12:05.000Z","uid":122,"like":19,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"5a04f5f3a3318e05b207ad7e65d07ff29df51a0b","tid":623370,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T02:51:01.000Z","msg":"【歐聯】不屑紅軍踢法 費蘭甸奴：咪又係長傳急攻<br />\n<br />\n曼城周二晚在歐聯8強次回合的生死戰主場迎戰利物浦，藍月亮中場費蘭甸奴賽前對紅軍的踢法嗤之以鼻，指利記不過是一支愛踢長傳急攻的球隊。<br />\n<br />\n該名巴西中場說：「他們是一支愛踢長傳急攻的球隊，總是把球員擠在球場中央。我希望我們能解決所有問題，特別是上半場，他們在10至15分鐘內就取得三個入球。保持不失球對我們是非常重要的，如果我們失一球，就要取得五個入球，所以我們得踢出自己的足球，也要球迷大力支持球隊，希望我們能完成工作。」"},{"pid":"34f04f1fc7bb5f1dd5d23c07aba252a4728320af","tid":623370,"uid":79711,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T02:51:50.000Z","msg":"講緊皇馬？"},{"pid":"3923b27163e458ee0bc14b5beb07dccd234e1cec","tid":623370,"uid":760,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T02:53:54.000Z","msg":"班鏝一輸就話人踢長波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f560c5b386d056afc942ef3d80298030eec5005f","tid":623370,"uid":46925,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T02:54:43.000Z","msg":"對住曼城唔通同你玩地面組織咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d010866bd79742cb6657f7780d41cfe979af807","tid":623370,"uid":96182,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T02:57:37.000Z","msg":"人人地好似講左句利鍾意玩longball就變左做不屑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以話報紙佬幾好搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"476dc8be635c6c69ecb742a19af53d7c9ec58377","tid":623370,"uid":31447,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"5d010866bd79742cb6657f7780d41cfe979af807","tid":623370,"uid":96182,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T02:57:37.000Z","msg":"人人地好似講左句利鍾意玩longball就變左做不屑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 